Application Components:
     Every application consists of three pillars 
      1.data storage- Workflow apps(opens new window) enable you to store data in Data tables and access your data through the Workflow apps connector.
      2. UI- The user interface for business users in Workflow apps portal. It is partially generated by Workato, and partially customized by creating Pages.
      3. Bussiness Logic- The logic of the application, implemented in Workato recipes.
     These three key components work together to create ease of building and an integrated user experience 
Data tables
     Workato Data Tables provide robust, scalable, and secure structured data storage in Workato. It enables you to define data tables in projects.
